	def apiCall(url):
		returnData = {"Success":False, "Data":None}
		startTime = system.date.now()
		headers = {'Api-Key': 'd03aad4cef083b478dd1c545aed06ecf'}
		baseUrl = "https://riti.breezechms.com"
		finalUrl = "%s%s"%(baseUrl, url)
		client = system.net.httpClient()
		response = client.get(url = finalUrl, headers = headers)
		endTime = system.date.now()
		if response.good:
			returnData["Success"] = True
			returnData["Data"] = response.json
		returnData["StartTime"] = startTime
		returnData["EndTime"] = endTime
		return returnData

	def listPeople():
		url = "/api/people?limit=100&details=1"
		result = apiCall(url)
		return result
	def listTags():
		url = "/api/tags/list_tags"
		result = apiCall(url)
		return result	
	
	def listVolunteers():	
		url = "/api/volunteers/list"
		result = apiCall(url)
		return result	
	self.view.getChild("root").custom.People = listPeople()
	self.view.getChild("root").custom.Tags = listTags()
	self.view.getChild("root").custom.Volunteers = listVolunteers()
